OL,3,C'I told white lies... but I didn't
OL,4,Ckill Natalie,' ex-partner tells murder
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FAn ex-partner of Natalie McNally has
OL,8,Ftold a court that he did not kill the
OL,9,FCo Armagh pregnant woman.
OL,11,FThe man, who cannot be named, also
OL,12,Ftold Belfast Crown Court that he did
OL,13,Fnot recruit someone else to kill Ms
OL,14,FMcNally, and denied that he had
OL,15,Finjured his hands on the night she was
OL,16,Fmurdered.
OL,18,FMs McNally, 32, was 15 weeks pregnant
OL,19,Fwhen she was killed at her home in
OL,20,FLurgan on 18 December 2022.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
