OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1773280992
OL,3,C'I told white lies... but I didn't
OL,4,Ckill Natalie,' ex-partner tells murder
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FHer partner, Stephen McCullagh, 36, of
OL,8,FWoodland Gardens in Lisburn, is on
OL,9,Ftrial for her murder.
OL,11,FHe has denied the charge.
OL,13,FThe ex-boyfriend had previously given
OL,14,Fevidence that he had told some "white
OL,15,Flies'" about the amount of contact he
OL,16,Fhad with Ms McNally when giving a
OL,17,Fpolice statement in the days after her
OL,18,Fdeath.
OL,26,@vD@`OUwD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
