FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1773280992
OL,3,C'I told white lies... but I didn't
OL,4,Ckill Natalie,' ex-partner tells murder
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FDefence barrister John Kearney KC
OL,8,Freturned to questioning him about the
OL,9,Fpolice interviews on Wednesday.
OL,11,FMr Kearney showed the witness
OL,12,Fphotographs of injuries to his hands
OL,13,Fduring the police interviews.
OL,15,FThe witness said he had sustained the
OL,16,Finjuries after punching walls.
OL,18,FThe barrister asked him if he was sure
OL,19,Fhe had not sustained the injuries on
OL,20,Fthe evening that Ms McNally was
OL,21,Fmurdered.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1773280992
OL,3,C'I told white lies... but I didn't
OL,4,Ckill Natalie,' ex-partner tells murder
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FHe responded: "No, I definitely didn't
OL,8,Fget them on that night."
OL,10,FMr Kearney said: "Was it you that
OL,11,Fkilled Natalie?"
OL,13,F"No," he said.
OL,15,FMr Kearney asked: "Were you present at
OL,16,FSilverwood (Green) on the 18th?"
OL,18,F"No," again the witness replied
OL,20,F"Did you recruit anyone else to help
OL,21,Fyou on the 18th?" the barrister asked.
