CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1773280992
OL,3,C'I told white lies... but I didn't
OL,4,Ckill Natalie,' ex-partner tells murder
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FThe witness again responded: "No."
OL,9,FThe barrister continued: "You
OL,10,Funderstand the defendant's case is
OL,11,Fthat he didn't do this, and he wasn't
OL,12,Fthere?"
OL,14,FThe witness said: "He done it."
OL,16,FHe then yelled towards McCullagh in
OL,17,Fthe court dock: "You done it."
OL,19,FMr Kearney said: "You understand that
OL,20,Fit was and remains his case that he
OL,21,Fbelieves it was you?"
OL,26,@oD@^OUoD@bO]qD@ZOUtD@GO]vD@SOUvD@_O]yD@
OL,26,AQOUyD@^O]{D@ROU}D@UO]
