OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1773280992
OL,3,C'I told white lies... but I didn't
OL,4,Ckill Natalie,' ex-partner tells murder
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,F"I understand that," he answered.
OL,9,F"Is that why you lied to police
OL,10,Finitially?" Mr Kearney asked.
OL,12,FThe witness said: "I told police the
OL,13,Ftruth, where I was, hour by hour for
OL,14,Ffour days.
OL,16,F"The only thing I lied about was when
OL,17,FI had last seen Natalie, which I
OL,18,Fcorrected when I was arrested ` and
OL,19,Fabout how much contact.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@TO]qD@AOUrD@KO]tD@SOUxD@AOU
