OL,3,C'I told white lies... but I didn't
OL,4,Ckill Natalie,' ex-partner tells murder
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,F"I told the truth as well as I could
OL,8,Fremember."
OL,10,FHe then turned again towards McCullagh
OL,11,Fand shouted: "You killed her."
OL,13,FThe trial continues.
